        "aq1": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I use any essential oil with the AutoLinkr Aroma?",
            "text": "<p>Yes — the AutoLinkr Aroma works with any standard essential oil or blend. You can use AutoLinkr scent cartridges for convenience, or fill the tank yourself with 5–10 drops of your preferred oil mixed with a small amount of water.</p>"
          }
        },
        "aq2": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is it safe to use while driving?",
            "text": "<p>Yes. The AutoLinkr Aroma emits a fine, cool mist at low volume — there is no visible fog, no heat, and no risk of distraction. It operates silently (under 25dB) and disperses scent gradually throughout the cabin without releasing any harsh fumes.</p>"
          }
        },
        "aq3": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How long do the scent cartridges last?",
            "text": "<p>Each AutoLinkr scent cartridge lasts approximately 30 days of standard use (assuming 1–2 hours of driving per day). Usage time will vary depending on your intensity setting and session frequency.</p>"
          }
        },
        "aq4": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Do I need to use the app to operate it?",
            "text": "<p>No. The AutoLinkr Aroma has a physical button on the device for basic on/off and intensity control. The app is optional and adds smart features like scheduling, timers, and intensity control from your phone.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
